WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
Speaker 1: Use the mouse to click on two matching tiles.

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Speaker 1: You have to start from the outside

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:08.000
Speaker 0: and select tiles that are around the edges.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:09.000
Speaker 0: When you've matched a pair,

00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:11.000
Speaker 0: it will disappear from the screen.

00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:14.000
Speaker 1: Keep going until all the tiles have been removed.

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:15.000
Speaker 1: Good luck.
